      "content": "it wasnt just a feeling though. it was like a physical pressure in my chest that hit exactly when the selling started. it feels more like a data stream than just \"psychosomatic\" stuff. if i can learn to interpret these sensations better, i could basically predict the spikes, right? it's like my nervous system is picking up on the high-frequency patterns.",
